-- native extern catalog slice 3 (typed gate): ePutStrLn via the typed pipeline.
-- ePutStrLn writes to stderr, which the gate drops via 2>/dev/null on both sides.
-- Oracle stdout: "()" (VUnit result).  Native stdout: "()" (mdk_print_unit).
-- Proves compile + link + run via the typed oracle path without stdout divergence.
main = ePutStrLn "err"
